    "name": "Happy Birthday: With Sergio Spellbound",
    "steam_appid": 3196290,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196290/extras/1d471890f0909ce33ec41313e4a2144e.apng?t=1730535743\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196290/extras/1d471890f0909ce33ec41313e4a2144e.poster.avif?t=1730535743\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=43 /></picture></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Birthday cards are OUT. Birthday games are IN.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gift this to your friends using the Steam gift functionality. You can buy it today and then schedule it to be delivered on their birthday. Easy right?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196290/extras/ef26f1d716d5891231ac3b622e3e1be1.apng?t=1730535743\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196290/extras/ef26f1d716d5891231ac3b622e3e1be1.poster.avif?t=1730535743\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=43 /></picture></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1.  Add to Cart.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2.  In the shopping cart, there is a drop down selection. Change the default option &quot;For My account&quot; to &quot;this is a gift&quot; (wow so generous!).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3.  Then click the button “Continue to gift options”.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4.  Choose the recipient of the gift.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5.  Provide a gift heartfelt birthday message (or not).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6.  Select &quot;schedule delivery&quot; and choose your friend's birthday. Or select &quot;As soon as  possible&quot; if it is already their special day.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7.  Proceed to purchase as normal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Done! Your chosen friend will receive their magical birthday gift on their birthday.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196290/extras/da2d75d9b752b0f650021c1a7f4533b0.apng?t=1730535743\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196290/extras/da2d75d9b752b0f650021c1a7f4533b0.poster.avif?t=1730535743\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=43 /></picture></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple endings based on your choices.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >15 minutes of delirious fun.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Point&amp;Click, Typing and Dance minigames.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unbelievable feats of magical skill.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An super exclusive private DJ dance party contained entirely in the virtual realm.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196290/extras/0cd167eb95250c540580b29df5fd1362.poster.avif?t=1730535743\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196290/extras/0cd167eb95250c540580b29df5fd1362.webm?t=1730535743\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196290/extras/0cd167eb95250c540580b29df5fd1362.mp4?t=1730535743\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
